proposed legislation to ensure the federal 
government complies with its own environmental laws is 
unconstitutional unneeded and could undercut efforts to clean up 
such facilities as the hanford nuclear reservation reagan 
administration officials said thursday 
members of a house subcommittee insisted however that the 
