shadows and a lot of doubt that suicide is like the measles you 
cant catch it 
even so bergenfield has worked hard to avoid any repeat of the 
tragedy 
in the past year bergenfield high school has given a parttime 
drug and alcohol counselor fulltime status authorities found 
traces of cocaine in the blood of all four of the dead youngsters 
and two had been drinking 
the school also hired a psychiatrist for grades 712 and hired 
two outreach workers for its community response team the response 
team comprised of mental health professionals clergy teachers 
and police officers began immediately after the suicides 
its an example of an outstanding response ms ross said 
theyve worked very hard we dont know how many suicides came 
close and were prevented 
bergenfields strategy will be part of a manual on adolescent 
