francois papa doc duvalier 
his father was a highranking member of the tontons macoute 
private militia it was organized by duvalier to throttle political 
opposition and challenge the power of the army which launched 
several coups against duvalier after his election in 1957 
pauls brother alexandre was haitis consul general to the 
