released on 250000 bond and promptly fled 
paul and his brother antonio face three drug counts conspiracy 
to distribute distribution and attempted importation of cocaine 
into the united states they could face up to 45 years in prison 
and 375000 in fines if they are convicted ms delinois was also 
indicted 
