announced the day the regulations were to take effect in response 
the administration ordered health and human services offices 
nationwide not to enforce the regulations 
the rules would have prevented federally funded family planning 
programs from providing abortion counseling abortion referrals 
and engaging in lobbying or legal action to increase availability 
of abortions 
